**Success Story Template:**
- Problem: Manual deployment causing 4-hour downtime
- Solution: Automated blue-green deployment pipeline
- Result: Zero-downtime deployments with 15-minute rollback
- Impact: 99.9% uptime improvement and faster feature delivery

